    public class CellInfo
extends Rectangle
    Information about a specific cell in a grid. Note: Whenever you change the instance variables that need to be stored in disk, you have to manually fix the implementation of class BlockListAsLongs
    Author:
    aseldawy

    • Field Detail

      • cellId

        public int cellId
        A unique ID for this cell in a file. This must be set initially when cells for a file are created. It cannot be guessed from cell dimensions.
